definition.text: Indicators are built by the Community! Usually, a developer will develop a few indicators he or she needs, and contribute them to the project in a new Data Mine!

paragraphs.text: The Community Data Mines Book is where you may find all existing data mines and their indicators! Each chapter in the book corresponds to a Data Mine...
Scan the contents of each chapter to get an idea of what is available at this point!
We'd love your data mine to be the next on the list!
